<P>FREEDOM From CIVIL and ECCLESIASTICAL SLAVERY, the purcha&s;e of CHRIST. A DISCOURSE, Offered to a numerous A&s;&s;embly, On <HI>MARCH</HI> the FIFTH, 1774, At the PRESBYTERIAN MEETING-HOUSE, in NEW-BURY-PORT. By <HI>Jonathan Par&s;ons,</HI> A. M. &amp; V. D. M.</P>
<P>NEW BURY-PORT, <HI>New-England:</HI> Printed by I. THOMAS and H. W. TINGES.</P>
