<P>TO THE Hon. JOHN HANCOCK, <ABBR>E&s;q</ABBR> OF <HI>BOSTON,</HI> The en&s;uing DISCOURSE is in&s;cribed By his humble &s;ervant, The AUTHOR.</P>
